<HR> <P>
<H2><A NAME=SECTION00132100000000000000> Translate Operation</A></H2>
<P>
	<A NAME=es5-tr HREF="es5-trbig.gif"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="" SRC="es5-tr.gif"></A>
	<A HREF="es5-trbig.gif">Figure (es5-tr): Translating an ARB5</A>
<P>
<tt>mged&gt; <em>Select the ``Translate'' entry in the solid edit menu</em> <BR>mged&gt; <em>p -1 -1 1</em> <BR>mged&gt;
</tt>
<P>
This command cause point 1 to be moved to coordinates (-1, -1, 1) and the
other points are moved so that they keep the same relative position to point
1.  See 
	<A HREF="es5-trbig.gif">Figure (es5-tr)</A>
.
<P>
Enter this command to restore the solid to it's original location:
<P>
<tt>mged&gt; <em>p 0 0 0</em> <BR>mged&gt;
</tt>
<P>
<HR>

